#. <section class="sutta" id="mn118"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn118:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 118"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 118"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn118:0.2"
msgid "Ānāpānassatisutta"
msgstr "Mindfulness of Breathing"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.79"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn118:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati pubbārāme migāramātupāsāde "
"sambahulehi abhiññātehi abhiññātehi therehi sāvakehi saddhiṃ—"
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in the Eastern Monastery, "
"the stilt longhouse of Migāra’s mother, together with several well-known "
"senior disciples, such as"

msgctxt "mn118:1.3"
msgid ""
"āyasmatā ca sāriputtena āyasmatā ca mahāmoggallānena āyasmatā ca "
"mahākassapena āyasmatā ca mahākaccāyanena āyasmatā ca mahākoṭṭhikena "
"āyasmatā ca mahākappinena āyasmatā ca mahācundena āyasmatā ca anuruddhena "
"āyasmatā ca revatena āyasmatā ca ānandena, aññehi ca abhiññātehi abhiññātehi "
"therehi sāvakehi saddhiṃ."
msgstr ""
"the venerables Sāriputta, Mahāmoggallāna, Mahākassapa, Mahākaccāna, "
"Mahākoṭṭhita, Mahākappina, Mahācunda, Anuruddha, Revata, Ānanda, and others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:2.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena therā bhikkhū nave bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the senior mendicants were advising and instructing the "
"junior mendicants."

msgctxt "mn118:2.2"
msgid ""
"Appekacce therā bhikkhū dasapi bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti, appekacce therā "
"bhikkhū vīsampi bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti, appekacce therā bhikkhū "
"tiṃsampi bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti, appekacce therā bhikkhū cattārīsampi "
"bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti."
msgstr ""
"Some senior mendicants instructed ten mendicants, while some instructed "
"twenty, thirty, or forty."

#. VAR: jānanti → pajānanti (bj, s1-3, km) | sañjānanti (mr)
msgctxt "mn118:2.3"
msgid ""
"Te ca navā bhikkhū therehi bhikkhūhi ovadiyamānā anusāsiyamānā uḷāraṃ "
"pubbenāparaṃ visesaṃ jānanti."
msgstr ""
"Being instructed by the senior mendicants, the junior mendicants realized a "
"higher distinction than they had before."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.80"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā tadahuposathe pannarase pavāraṇāya puṇṇāya "
"puṇṇamāya rattiyā bhikkhusaṃghaparivuto abbhokāse nisinno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now, at that time it was the sabbath—the full moon on the fifteenth day—and "
"the Buddha was sitting surrounded by the Saṅgha of monks for the invitation "
"to admonish."

msgctxt "mn118:3.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tuṇhībhūtaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ bhikkhusaṃghaṃ anuviloketvā bhikkhū "
"āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha looked around the Saṅgha of monks, who were so very silent. "
"He addressed them:"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:4.1"
msgid "“āraddhosmi, bhikkhave, imāya paṭipadāya;"
msgstr "“I am satisfied, mendicants, with this practice."

msgctxt "mn118:4.2"
msgid "āraddhacittosmi, bhikkhave, imāya paṭipadāya."
msgstr "My heart is satisfied with this practice."

msgctxt "mn118:4.3"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, bhiyyoso mattāya vīriyaṃ ārabhatha appattassa pattiyā, "
"anadhigatassa adhigamāya, asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya."
msgstr ""
"So you should rouse up even more energy for attaining the unattained, "
"achieving the unachieved, and realizing the unrealized."

msgctxt "mn118:4.4"
msgid "Idhevāhaṃ sāvatthiyaṃ komudiṃ cātumāsiniṃ āgamessāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"I will wait here in Sāvatthī for the Komudi full moon of the fourth month.”"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:5.1"
msgid "Assosuṃ kho jānapadā bhikkhū:"
msgstr "Mendicants from around the country heard about this."

msgctxt "mn118:5.2"
msgid "“bhagavā kira tattheva sāvatthiyaṃ komudiṃ cātumāsiniṃ āgamessatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sāvatthiṃ → sāvatthiyaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "mn118:5.3"
msgid "Te jānapadā bhikkhū sāvatthiṃ osaranti bhagavantaṃ dassanāya."
msgstr "They came down to Sāvatthī to see the Buddha."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:6.1"
msgid ""
"Te ca kho therā bhikkhū bhiyyoso mattāya nave bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti."
msgstr "And those senior mendicants instructed the junior mendicants even more."

msgctxt "mn118:6.2"
msgid ""
"Appekacce therā bhikkhū dasapi bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti, appekacce therā "
"bhikkhū vīsampi bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti, appekacce therā bhikkhū "
"tiṃsampi bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti, appekacce therā bhikkhū cattārīsampi "
"bhikkhū ovadanti anusāsanti."
msgstr ""
"Some senior mendicants instructed ten mendicants, while some instructed "
"twenty, thirty, or forty."

msgctxt "mn118:6.3"
msgid ""
"Te ca navā bhikkhū therehi bhikkhūhi ovadiyamānā anusāsiyamānā uḷāraṃ "
"pubbenāparaṃ visesaṃ jānanti."
msgstr ""
"Being instructed by the senior mendicants, the junior mendicants realized a "
"higher distinction than they had before."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:7.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā tadahuposathe pannarase komudiyā cātumāsiniyā "
"puṇṇāya puṇṇamāya rattiyā bhikkhusaṅghaparivuto abbhokāse nisinno hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now, at that time it was the sabbath—the Komudi full moon on the fifteenth "
"day of the fourth month—and the Buddha was sitting in the open surrounded by "
"the Saṅgha of monks."

msgctxt "mn118:7.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tuṇhībhūtaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ anuviloketvā bhikkhū "
"āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha looked around the Saṅgha of monks, who were so very silent. "
"He addressed them:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: suddhā sāre → suddhasāre patiṭṭhitā (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn118:8.1"
msgid ""
"“Apalāpāyaṃ, bhikkhave, parisā; nippalāpāyaṃ, bhikkhave, parisā; suddhā sāre "
"patiṭṭhitā."
msgstr ""
"“This assembly has no nonsense, mendicants, it’s free of nonsense. It "
"consists purely of the essential core."

msgctxt "mn118:8.2"
msgid ""
"Tathārūpo ayaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhusaṃgho; tathārūpā ayaṃ, bhikkhave, parisā"
msgstr "Such is this Saṅgha of monks, such is this assembly!"

msgctxt "mn118:8.3"
msgid ""
"yathārūpā parisā āhuneyyā pāhuneyyā dakkhiṇeyyā añjalikaraṇīyā anuttaraṃ "
"puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""
"An assembly such as this is worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, "
"worthy of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’s offering, worthy of greeting "
"with joined palms, and is the supreme field of merit for the world."

msgctxt "mn118:8.4"
msgid ""
"Tathārūpo ayaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhusaṃgho; tathārūpā ayaṃ, bhikkhave, parisā"
msgstr "Such is this Saṅgha of monks, such is this assembly!"

msgctxt "mn118:8.5"
msgid "yathārūpāya parisāya appaṃ dinnaṃ bahu hoti, bahu dinnaṃ bahutaraṃ."
msgstr ""
"Even a small gift to an assembly such as this is fruitful, while giving more "
"is even more fruitful."

msgctxt "mn118:8.6"
msgid ""
"Tathārūpo ayaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhusaṃgho; tathārūpā ayaṃ, bhikkhave, parisā"
msgstr "Such is this Saṅgha of monks, such is this assembly!"

msgctxt "mn118:8.7"
msgid "yathārūpā parisā dullabhā dassanāya lokassa."
msgstr "An assembly such as this is rarely seen in the world."

msgctxt "mn118:8.8"
msgid ""
"Tathārūpo ayaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhusaṃgho; tathārūpā ayaṃ, bhikkhave, parisā"
msgstr "Such is this Saṅgha of monks, such is this assembly!"

#. VAR: puṭosenāpi → pūtaṃsenāpi tathārūpo ayaṃ bhikkhave bhikkhusaṃgho tathārūpā’yaṃ bhikkhave parisā (s1) | pūṭaṃsenāpi (s2, s3) | puṭosenāpi tathārūpo ayaṃ bhikkhave bhikkhusaṃgho tathārūpā’yaṃ bhikkhave parisā (pts1) | tathārūpā ayaṃ parisā (mr)
msgctxt "mn118:8.9"
msgid "yathārūpaṃ parisaṃ alaṃ yojanagaṇanāni dassanāya gantuṃ puṭosenāpi."
msgstr ""
"An assembly such as this is worth traveling many leagues to see, even if you "
"have to carry your own provisions in a shoulder bag."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.81"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:9.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe arahanto khīṇāsavā "
"vusitavanto katakaraṇīyā ohitabhārā anuppattasadatthā "
"parikkhīṇabhavasaṃyojanā sammadaññāvimuttā—"
msgstr ""
"For in this Saṅgha there are perfected mendicants, who have ended the "
"defilements, completed the spiritual journey, done what had to be done, laid "
"down the burden, achieved their own goal, utterly ended the fetters of "
"rebirth, and are rightly freed through enlightenment."

msgctxt "mn118:9.2"
msgid "evarūpāpi, bhikkhave, santi bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe."
msgstr "There are such mendicants in this Saṅgha."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:10.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ "
"saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā opapātikā tattha parinibbāyino anāvattidhammā tasmā "
"lokā—"
msgstr ""
"In this Saṅgha there are mendicants who, with the ending of the five lower "
"fetters are reborn spontaneously. They are extinguished there, and are not "
"liable to return from that world."

msgctxt "mn118:10.2"
msgid "evarūpāpi, bhikkhave, santi bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe."
msgstr "There are such mendicants in this Saṅgha."

#. VAR: sakideva → sakiṃdeva (mr)
msgctxt "mn118:10.3"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ "
"parikkhayā rāgadosamohānaṃ tanuttā sakadāgāmino sakideva imaṃ lokaṃ āgantvā "
"dukkhassantaṃ karissanti—"
msgstr ""
"In this Saṅgha there are mendicants who, with the ending of three fetters, "
"and the weakening of greed, hate, and delusion, are once-returners. They "
"come back to this world once only, then make an end of suffering."

msgctxt "mn118:10.4"
msgid "evarūpāpi, bhikkhave, santi bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe."
msgstr "There are such mendicants in this Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn118:10.5"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ "
"parikkhayā sotāpannā avinipātadhammā niyatā sambodhiparāyanā—"
msgstr ""
"In this Saṅgha there are mendicants who, with the ending of three fetters "
"are stream-enterers, not liable to be reborn in the underworld, bound for "
"awakening."

msgctxt "mn118:10.6"
msgid "evarūpāpi, bhikkhave, santi bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṃghe."
msgstr "There are such mendicants in this Saṅgha."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.82"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:13.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ "
"bhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti—"
msgstr ""
"In this Saṅgha there are mendicants who are committed to developing the four "
"kinds of mindfulness meditation …"

msgctxt "mn118:13.2"
msgid "evarūpāpi, bhikkhave, santi bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:14.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe catunnaṃ sammappadhānānaṃ "
"bhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti … pe …"
msgstr "the four right efforts …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.2"
msgid "catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ …"
msgstr "the four bases of psychic power …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.3"
msgid "pañcannaṃ indriyānaṃ …"
msgstr "the five faculties …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.4"
msgid "pañcannaṃ balānaṃ …"
msgstr "the five powers …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.5"
msgid "sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ …"
msgstr "the seven awakening factors …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.6"
msgid "ariyassa aṭṭhaṅgikassa maggassa bhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti—"
msgstr "the noble eightfold path."

msgctxt "mn118:14.7"
msgid "evarūpāpi, bhikkhave, santi bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe."
msgstr "There are such mendicants in this Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn118:14.8"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe mettābhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā "
"viharanti …"
msgstr ""
"In this Saṅgha there are mendicants who are committed to developing the "
"meditation on love …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.9"
msgid "karuṇābhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti …"
msgstr "compassion …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.10"
msgid "muditābhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti …"
msgstr "rejoicing …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.11"
msgid "upekkhābhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti …"
msgstr "equanimity …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.12"
msgid "asubhabhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti …"
msgstr "ugliness …"

msgctxt "mn118:14.13"
msgid "aniccasaññābhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti—"
msgstr "impermanence."

msgctxt "mn118:14.14"
msgid "evarūpāpi, bhikkhave, santi bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe."
msgstr "There are such mendicants in this Saṅgha."

msgctxt "mn118:14.15"
msgid ""
"Santi, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmiṃ bhikkhusaṅghe "
"ānāpānassatibhāvanānuyogamanuyuttā viharanti."
msgstr ""
"In this Saṅgha there are mendicants who are committed to developing the "
"meditation on mindfulness of breathing."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:15.1"
msgid ""
"Ānāpānassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti mahānisaṃsā."
msgstr ""
"Mendicants, when mindfulness of breathing is developed and cultivated it is "
"very fruitful and beneficial."

msgctxt "mn118:15.2"
msgid ""
"Ānāpānassati, bhikkhave, bhāvitā bahulīkatā cattāro satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti."
msgstr ""
"Mindfulness of breathing, when developed and cultivated, fulfills the four "
"kinds of mindfulness meditation."

msgctxt "mn118:15.3"
msgid "Cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta bojjhaṅge paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"The four kinds of mindfulness meditation, when developed and cultivated, "
"fulfill the seven awakening factors."

msgctxt "mn118:15.4"
msgid "Satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ paripūrenti."
msgstr ""
"And the seven awakening factors, when developed and cultivated, fulfill "
"knowledge and freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:16.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati kathaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated to be very "
"fruitful and beneficial?"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:17.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā rukkhamūlagato vā suññāgāragato vā "
"nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ "
"upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has gone to a wilderness, or to the root of a tree, or "
"to an empty hut. They sit down cross-legged, with their body straight, and "
"establish mindfulness right there."

#. VAR: satova → sato (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "mn118:17.2"
msgid "So satova assasati satova passasati."
msgstr "Just mindful, they breathe in. Mindful, they breathe out."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya18"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:18.1"
msgid ""
"Dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto ‘"
"dīghaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"When breathing in heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing in heavily.’ When "
"breathing out heavily they know: ‘I’m breathing out heavily.’"

msgctxt "mn118:18.2"
msgid ""
"rassaṃ vā assasanto ‘rassaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti, rassaṃ vā passasanto ‘"
"rassaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr ""
"When breathing in lightly they know: ‘I’m breathing in lightly.’ When "
"breathing out lightly they know: ‘I’m breathing out lightly.’"

msgctxt "mn118:18.3"
msgid ""
"‘sabbakāyapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sabbakāyapaṭisaṃvedī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in experiencing the whole body. They practice "
"breathing out experiencing the whole body."

msgctxt "mn118:18.4"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"kāyasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati. (1)"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in stilling the body’s motion. They practice "
"breathing out stilling the body’s motion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya19"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.83"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:19.1"
msgid ""
"‘Pītipaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘pītipaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in experiencing rapture. They practice breathing out "
"experiencing rapture."

msgctxt "mn118:19.2"
msgid ""
"‘sukhapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sukhapaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in experiencing bliss. They practice breathing out "
"experiencing bliss."

msgctxt "mn118:19.3"
msgid ""
"‘cittasaṅkhārapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘cittasaṅkhārapaṭisaṃvedī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in experiencing these emotions. They practice "
"breathing out experiencing these emotions."

msgctxt "mn118:19.4"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ cittasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"cittasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati. (2)"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in stilling these emotions. They practice breathing "
"out stilling these emotions."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:20.1"
msgid ""
"‘Cittapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘cittapaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in experiencing the mind. They practice breathing "
"out experiencing the mind."

msgctxt "mn118:20.2"
msgid ""
"‘abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in gladdening the mind. They practice breathing out "
"gladdening the mind."

msgctxt "mn118:20.3"
msgid ""
"‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in immersing the mind in samādhi. They practice "
"breathing out immersing the mind in samādhi."

msgctxt "mn118:20.4"
msgid ""
"‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati. (3)"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in freeing the mind. They practice breathing out "
"freeing the mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:21.1"
msgid ""
"‘Aniccānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘aniccānupassī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in observing impermanence. They practice breathing "
"out observing impermanence."

msgctxt "mn118:21.2"
msgid ""
"‘virāgānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘virāgānupassī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in observing fading away. They practice breathing "
"out observing fading away."

msgctxt "mn118:21.3"
msgid ""
"‘nirodhānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘nirodhānupassī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in observing cessation. They practice breathing out "
"observing cessation."

msgctxt "mn118:21.4"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati."
msgstr ""
"They practice breathing in observing letting go. They practice breathing out "
"observing letting go."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:22.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati evaṃ bahulīkatā mahapphalā hoti "
"mahānisaṃsā. (4)"
msgstr ""
"Mindfulness of breathing, when developed and cultivated in this way, is very "
"fruitful and beneficial."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya23"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:23.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati kathaṃ bahulīkatā cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill the four kinds of mindfulness meditation?"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya24"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:24.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu dīghaṃ vā assasanto ‘dīghaṃ assasāmī’ti "
"pajānāti, dīghaṃ vā passasanto ‘dīghaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr "Whenever a mendicant knows that they breathe heavily,"

msgctxt "mn118:24.2"
msgid ""
"rassaṃ vā assasanto ‘rassaṃ assasāmī’ti pajānāti, rassaṃ vā passasanto ‘"
"rassaṃ passasāmī’ti pajānāti;"
msgstr "or lightly,"

msgctxt "mn118:24.3"
msgid ""
"‘sabbakāyapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sabbakāyapaṭisaṃvedī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "or experiencing the whole body,"

msgctxt "mn118:24.4"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ kāyasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"kāyasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "or stilling the body’s motion—"

msgctxt "mn118:24.5"
msgid ""
"kāye kāyānupassī, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"at that time they’re meditating by observing an aspect of the body—keen, "
"aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "mn118:24.6"
msgid "Kāyesu kāyaññatarāhaṃ, bhikkhave, evaṃ vadāmi yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsā."
msgstr ""
"For I say that the in-breaths and out-breaths are an aspect of the body."

msgctxt "mn118:24.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, kāye kāyānupassī tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (1)"
msgstr ""
"That’s why at that time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of "
"the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya25"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.84"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:25.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘pītipaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘"
"pītipaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "Whenever a mendicant practices breathing while experiencing rapture,"

msgctxt "mn118:25.2"
msgid ""
"‘sukhapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘sukhapaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr "or experiencing bliss,"

msgctxt "mn118:25.3"
msgid ""
"‘cittasaṅkhārapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘cittasaṅkhārapaṭisaṃvedī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "or experiencing these emotions,"

msgctxt "mn118:25.4"
msgid ""
"‘passambhayaṃ cittasaṅkhāraṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘passambhayaṃ "
"cittasaṅkhāraṃ passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "or stilling these emotions—"

msgctxt "mn118:25.5"
msgid ""
"vedanāsu vedanānupassī, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"at that time they meditate observing an aspect of feelings—keen, aware, and "
"mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "mn118:25.6"
msgid ""
"Vedanāsu vedanāññatarāhaṃ, bhikkhave, evaṃ vadāmi yadidaṃ—assāsapassāsānaṃ "
"sādhukaṃ manasikāraṃ."
msgstr ""
"For I say that close attention to the in-breaths and out-breaths is an "
"aspect of feelings."

msgctxt "mn118:25.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, vedanāsu vedanānupassī tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati "
"ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (2)"
msgstr ""
"That’s why at that time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of "
"feelings—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya26"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:26.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘cittapaṭisaṃvedī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, "
"‘cittapaṭisaṃvedī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "Whenever a mendicant practices breathing while experiencing the mind,"

msgctxt "mn118:26.2"
msgid ""
"‘abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘abhippamodayaṃ cittaṃ "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "or gladdening the mind,"

msgctxt "mn118:26.3"
msgid ""
"‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘samādahaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr "or immersing the mind in samādhi,"

msgctxt "mn118:26.4"
msgid ""
"‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘vimocayaṃ cittaṃ passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr "or freeing the mind—"

msgctxt "mn118:26.5"
msgid ""
"citte cittānupassī, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"at that time they meditate observing an aspect of the mind—keen, aware, and "
"mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "mn118:26.6"
msgid "Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, muṭṭhassatissa asampajānassa ānāpānassatiṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"There is no development of mindfulness of breathing for someone who is "
"unmindful and lacks awareness, I say."

msgctxt "mn118:26.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, citte cittānupassī tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati "
"ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (3)"
msgstr ""
"That’s why at that time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of "
"the mind—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya27"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.85"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:27.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ‘aniccānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘"
"aniccānupassī passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "Whenever a mendicant practices breathing while observing impermanence,"

msgctxt "mn118:27.2"
msgid ""
"‘virāgānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘virāgānupassī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr "or observing fading away,"

msgctxt "mn118:27.3"
msgid ""
"‘nirodhānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘nirodhānupassī passasissāmī’ti "
"sikkhati;"
msgstr "or observing cessation,"

msgctxt "mn118:27.4"
msgid ""
"‘paṭinissaggānupassī assasissāmī’ti sikkhati, ‘paṭinissaggānupassī "
"passasissāmī’ti sikkhati;"
msgstr "or observing letting go—"

msgctxt "mn118:27.5"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati ātāpī "
"sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"at that time they meditate observing an aspect of principles—keen, aware, "
"and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "mn118:27.6"
msgid ""
"So yaṃ taṃ abhijjhādomanassānaṃ pahānaṃ taṃ paññāya disvā sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""
"Having seen with wisdom the giving up of desire and aversion, they watch "
"over closely with equanimity."

msgctxt "mn118:27.7"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, dhammesu dhammānupassī tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu viharati "
"ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. (4)"
msgstr ""
"That’s why at that time a mendicant is meditating by observing an aspect of "
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya28"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:28.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, ānāpānassati evaṃ bahulīkatā cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how mindfulness of breathing, when developed and cultivated, fulfills "
"the four kinds of mindfulness meditation."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:29.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā kathaṃ bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti?"
msgstr ""
"And how are the four kinds of mindfulness meditation developed and "
"cultivated so as to fulfill the seven awakening factors?"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya30"></a>
#. VAR: asammuṭṭhā → appamuṭṭhā (s1) | appammuṭṭhā (s2, s3, km)
msgctxt "mn118:30.1"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno "
"satimā vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ, upaṭṭhitāssa tasmiṃ samaye sati hoti "
"asammuṭṭhā."
msgstr ""
"Whenever a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body, at that "
"time their mindfulness is established and lucid."

msgctxt "mn118:30.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno upaṭṭhitā sati hoti asammuṭṭhā, "
"satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti. Satisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (1)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"mindfulness; they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya31"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
#. VAR: pavicayati → pavicarati (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "mn118:31.1"
msgid ""
"So tathāsato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinati pavicayati "
"parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""
"As they live mindfully in this way they investigate, explore, and inquire "
"into that principle with wisdom."

msgctxt "mn118:31.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tathāsato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya "
"pavicinati pavicayati parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjati, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ "
"samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye "
"bhikkhu bhāveti, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (2)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"investigation of principles; they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya32"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:32.1"
msgid ""
"Tassa taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato pavicayato parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjato "
"āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ."
msgstr ""
"As they investigate principles with wisdom in this way their energy is "
"roused up and unflagging."

msgctxt "mn118:32.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato "
"pavicayato parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjato āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ, "
"vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (3)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of energy; "
"they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya33"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.86"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:33.1"
msgid "Āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti nirāmisā."
msgstr "When they’re energetic, spiritual rapture arises."

msgctxt "mn118:33.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti "
"nirāmisā, pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"pītisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ "
"samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (4)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of rapture; "
"they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya34"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:34.1"
msgid "Pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi passambhati."
msgstr "When the mind is full of rapture, the body and mind become tranquil."

msgctxt "mn118:34.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi "
"passambhati, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (5)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"tranquility; they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya35"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:35.1"
msgid "Passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""
"When the body is tranquil and they feel bliss, the mind becomes immersed in "
"samādhi."

msgctxt "mn118:35.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ "
"samādhiyati, samādhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"samādhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, samādhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (6)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of immersion; "
"they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya36"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:36.1"
msgid "So tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr "They closely watch over that mind immersed in samādhi."

msgctxt "mn118:36.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho "
"hoti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (7)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of equanimity;"
" they develop it and perfect it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya37"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:37.1"
msgid "Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "Whenever a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of feelings …"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya38"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:38.1"
msgid "citte …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "mn118:38.2"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ, upaṭṭhitāssa tasmiṃ samaye sati hoti asammuṭṭhā."
msgstr "principles, at that time their mindfulness is established and lucid."

msgctxt "mn118:38.3"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno upaṭṭhitā sati hoti asammuṭṭhā, "
"satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, satisambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, satisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (1)"
msgstr ""
"At such a time, a mendicant has activated the awakening factor of "
"mindfulness …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.87"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc27"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:38.4"
msgid ""
"So tathāsato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinati pavicayati "
"parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn118:38.5"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tathāsato viharanto taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya "
"pavicinati pavicayati parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjati, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ "
"samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye "
"bhikkhu bhāveti, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (2)"
msgstr "investigation of principles …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:38.6"
msgid ""
"Tassa taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato pavicayato parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjato "
"āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn118:38.7"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno taṃ dhammaṃ paññāya pavicinato "
"pavicayato parivīmaṃsaṃ āpajjato āraddhaṃ hoti vīriyaṃ asallīnaṃ, "
"vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, vīriyasambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (3)"
msgstr "energy …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:38.8"
msgid "Āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti nirāmisā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn118:38.9"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno āraddhavīriyassa uppajjati pīti "
"nirāmisā, pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"pītisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, pītisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ "
"samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (4)"
msgstr "rapture …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc30"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:38.10"
msgid "Pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi passambhati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn118:38.11"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pītimanassa kāyopi passambhati, cittampi "
"passambhati, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (5)"
msgstr "tranquility …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc31"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:38.12"
msgid "Passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn118:38.13"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno passaddhakāyassa sukhino cittaṃ "
"samādhiyati, samādhisambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho hoti, "
"samādhisambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, samādhisambojjhaṅgo "
"tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati. (6)"
msgstr "immersion …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya39"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc32"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:39.1"
msgid "So tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ ajjhupekkhitā hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn118:39.2"
msgid ""
"Yasmiṃ samaye, bhikkhave, bhikkhu tathāsamāhitaṃ cittaṃ sādhukaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitā hoti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno āraddho "
"hoti, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhu bhāveti, "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhuno bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr "equanimity."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya40"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:40.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā evaṃ bahulīkatā satta "
"sambojjhaṅge paripūrenti. (7)"
msgstr ""
"That’s how the four kinds of mindfulness meditation, when developed and "
"cultivated, fulfill the seven awakening factors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya41"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.88"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc33"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:41.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvitā ca, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā kathaṃ bahulīkatā "
"vijjāvimuttiṃ paripūrenti?"
msgstr ""
"And how are the seven awakening factors developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill knowledge and freedom?"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya42"></a>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya43"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:42.1"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ "
"virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. Dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgaṃ "
"bhāveti … pe … vīriyasambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … pītisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … "
"passaddhisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … samādhisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti … "
"upekkhāsambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the awakening factors of mindfulness, "
"investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and "
"equanimity, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen "
"as letting go."

msgctxt "mn118:42.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā evaṃ bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrentī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how the seven awakening factors, when developed and cultivated, "
"fulfill knowledge and freedom.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc34"></a>
msgctxt "mn118:42.3"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn118:42.4"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti."
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn118:42.5"
msgid "Ānāpānassatisuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
